 class=\"screenreader-only\">Download Slides</span></a></span> from the Sept. 24 lecture&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Midterm exam</strong> information</span>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Monday, October 13 at 10:10 am on Canvas</strong>: <a title=\"Midterm Exam\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/124722/quizzes/483588\" data-course-type=\"quizzes\" data-published=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/124722/quizzes/483588\" data-api-returntype=\"Quiz\">exam link</a></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">. <strong>The exam ends at 11 am no matter when you start!</strong>&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Topics covered: I.A. Intro; II. A. (Neo)Realism; II.B. (Neo)liberalism; and II.C. Marxism. </span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Use the&nbsp;</span><span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\"><a class=\"inline_disabled preview_in_overlay\" title=\"Midterm Exam Lecture Slides.pdf\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/124722/files/80990605?wrap=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-canvas-previewable=\"false\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/124722/files/80990605\" data-api-returntype=\"File\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">lecture slides</span></a><a class=\"file_download_btn\" role=\"button\" download=\"\" style=\"margin-inline-start: 5px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/124722/files/80990605/download?download_frd=1\"><span role=\"presentation\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1920\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"m1807.093 1482.477 79.736 79.963-355.313 355.312H355.346L.035 1562.44l79.85-79.963 322.22 322.334H1484.76l322.334-322.334ZM997.677-.033v1167.02l355.313-355.313 79.962 79.85-491.858 491.633L449.46 891.524l79.962-79.85 355.313 355.313V-.033h1